{"tid":90062,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解你唔肯原諒我？","createTime":"2017-01-21T18:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T14:38:48.000Z","uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7f1d1cbdb95c60b70509281239fc96deb6a054c","tid":90062,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:15:32.000Z","msg":"都過左咁耐啦<br />\n點解你仲未嬲完？<br />\n點解你要咁執著？<br />\n唔係話做唔成情侶都可以做朋友咩？<br />\n點解你連朋友都唔想同我做？<br />\n我到底做錯左d咩野？<br />\n你幾時先肯原諒我？<br />\n好掛住你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但明明我都冇做錯<br />\n我錯左係邊度？<br />\n你憑咩嬲我？ 點解仲要我講對唔住？<br />\n仲要講極對唔住你都係唔滿意？<br />\n你要點先肯原諒我？<br />\n我覺得自己連兵都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知你叻 我配唔起你 你係娘娘多一隻兵唔多<br />\n我都係想和平d姐 好來好去咁唔好咩？<br />\n到底你要幾時先肯放下憤怒？<br />\n我唔明白 乜時間唔係可以解決一切問題咩？<br />\n到底要隔幾耐 你先可以釋懷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702511d44cc8692a8e9421c84acebff39f97fe00","tid":90062,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:16:28.000Z","msg":"咪煩啦！男人老狗嘈到上黎開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分手啦"},{"pid":"e265af0b9c5d7ac8cbe73de04ece308f7d9dccd1","tid":90062,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:19:14.000Z","msg":"點解要原諒你"},{"pid":"9dfd9bf48f159b97a2736b3c84705a8f8e998096","tid":90062,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:22:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪煩啦！男人老狗嘈到上黎開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分手啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同佢有太多共同朋友<br />\n唔敢同朋友講<br />\n唯有同你地講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06dbe9d35be4a5e2ea92862d913a6a98d0da11e","tid":90062,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:22